cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for sentiment analysis and public health applications. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of attention mechanisms and multiple instance learning, which are common techniques in machine learning and deep learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Finally, the paper discusses the application of the proposed model in public health, which could fall under the category of social and information sciences (cs.SI).
